http://www.empower.org:80/heritage/library/categories/natsec/bg1074.html 204.71.237.79 19970210031809 text/html 46257
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 10-Feb-97 03:18:50 GMT
Last-modified: Wednesday, 20-Mar-96 14:48:52 GMT
