<I>Newsweek</I>,  January 15, 1996, p. 23.
<p>
<li>Hillary Rodham Clinton, op. cit., p. 53.
<p>
<li>Brant and Thomas, <I>Newsweek</I>, p. 23.
<p>
<li>Hillary Rodham Clinton, op. cit., p. 32.
<p>
