http://www.empower.org:80/heritage/p_review/jan96/meese.html 204.71.237.79 19970210035327 text/html 27723
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 10-Feb-97 03:54:10 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 11-Jan-96 22:41:16 GMT
Content-length: 27537
