<head>
<title>Leadership Institute 1996 Training Schedule</title>
</head>
<body>
<center>
<img src="/lead-inst/sc-logo.gif"><br>
<h3>1997<br>
School Schedule</h3>
<hr width=30%><P>
<b>
<p>

</b>
</center>
<pre>
<B>
<B>January</B>
	13		Resume Workshop and Job Fair
	30-31		<a href="/lead-inst/sc-ch.html">Capitol Hill Staff Training School</a>

