<center>
<h2>Results from Town Hall - Compuserve Presidential Poll</h2>
</center>
<b>The following poll was taken on the Town Hall CompuServe site.  To access the CompuServe Town Hall, type GO! TOWNHALL on CompuServe.
<p>
<hr></b>
<pre>
Town Hall, the Conservative Meeting Place on CompuServe, is pleased to 
announce the results of its first "Road to '96" survey. With over 4500 
self-described conservative members from across the county, Town Hall 
and its participating organizations are committed to educating and 
informing at the grassroots level.


Results of Town Hall's "Road to '96" survey. 
 (Numbers may not add to 100% due to rounding) 
 
Q) If the GOP primary were held today, you would vote for: 
 
Phil Gramm		25% 
