<html>
<title>Policy Review Fall 1995: Table of Contents</title>
<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="/heritage/paperh.jpg">
<h2><center><img src="/heritage/revpo.gif" alt="Policy Review" border=0><p><font size="+3">T</font>ABLE OF <FONT SIZE="+3">C</FONT>ONTENTS</H2>
<HR SIZE=3 WIDTH=50%>
<b><a href="/heritage/p_review/welcome.html">Policy Review</a> </b><br>
<i>No. 74  Fall 1995</I><p>
<hr>
<P>
<a href="thegg.html">The Beat Generation</a> <br>Community policing at its best<br>
By William D. Eggers & John O'Leary
<p>
<a href="thiuli.html">Arresting Ideas</a><br>Tougher law enforcement is driving down urban crime<br>
By John J. DiIulio Jr.<p>
						
<a href="thflah.html">Legal Disservices Corp.</a><br>
There are better ways to provide legal aid to the poor<br>By Kenneth F. Boehm & Peter T. Flaherty<p>

<a href="thmcgin.html">Original Thomas, Conventional Souter</a><br>What kind of justices should the next president pick?<br>
