HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 10-Feb-97 04:45:30 GMT
Last-modified: Friday, 20-Oct-95 14:26:49 GMT
Content-length: 1009
Content-type: text/html
</DOCHDR>
<html>
