http://www.empower.org:80/nmp/wr-9-95.html 204.71.237.79 19970210045043 text/html 13222
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 10-Feb-97 04:51:27 GMT
Last-modified: Friday, 20-Oct-95 14:26:00 GMT
Content-length: 13038
Content-type: text/html
</DOCHDR>
