<html><head><title>The Town Hall QuickPoll</title></head>

<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="/townhall/background.jpg">

<blockquote><center>

<a href="/cgi-bin/redir?SpaceID=16&AdID=17&URL=http://pinpoint121.com/cgi-bin/pinpoint/welcome%3Ftownhall"><img src="/ads/pinpoint/Pinpoint.gif" border=0 width=110 height=120 alt="Take our survey: You may win a prize!"></a>

<a href="/cgi-bin/redir?SpaceID=17&AdID=21&URL=http://www.townhall.com/townhall/columnists/otb"><img src="/ads/house/otbblue.gif" border=0 width=110 height=120 alt="Click for commentary from across the country!"></a>

<a href="/cgi-bin/redir?SpaceID=18&AdID=24&URL=http://www.townhall.com/thcc"><img src="/ads/house/electhcc.gif" border=0 width=110 height=120 alt="Light up your day with The Current!"></a>

<h2>The Town Hall QuickPoll</h2></center>

<center><form action="/townhall/infotain/vote/quickpoll.cgi" method="post"><br>

Do you believe the unborn child has a "right to life"?

<p>

<input type="radio" name="question" value="Yes"> Yes <br>

<input type="radio" name="question" value="Undecided"> Undecided <br>

<input type="radio" name="question" value="No"> No <br>

<p><input type="submit" value="Cast your vote"></form><p><br><p>

<h3>Archive of the past seven questions:</h3><p>

Do U.S. Citizens have a right to assisted suicide?

<br>

Yes: 33%<br>

Undecided: 5%<br>

No: 62%<br>


<p>

Should Newt pay the fine from his campaign funds?

<br>

Yes: 61%<br>

Undecided: 6%<br>

No: 31%<br>


<p>

Has the O.J. Simpson affair changed your view of the judicial system?

<br>

Yes: 57%<br>

Undecided: 1%<br>

No: 41%<br>


<p>

Is Campaign Finance Reform on your list of top priorities?

<br>

Yes: 24%<br>

Undecided: 0%<br>

No: 75%<br>


<p>

Has Wayne LaPierre done a good job running the NRA?

<br>

Yes: 65%<br>

No: 20%<br>

Undecided: 13%<br>


<p>

Should the Senate spend over 6 million dollars investigating Clinton?

<br>

Yes: 82%<br>

Undecided: 0%<br>

No: 17%<br>


<p>

Would you support a commuter tax for Virginia/Maryland residents who work in D.C.?

<br>

Yes: 33%<br>

Undecided: 0%<br>

No: 66%<br>


<p><br>


<center>

<a href="/townhall/tbut.map"><img src="/townhall/tbut.gif" ISMAP border="0"></a>

</center>



</center></blockquote></body></html>

